Halo's Capture the flag map is now a CSS
deathmatch map!

There are some changes to the size of the 
map, this is due to the difference in POV 
and jumping distances in CSS.

And what are those big orange things?
Go have a look!


Hangumrealhigh mods include

-------------------------------------

new uppers levels
4 more teleporters [6 in all now]
new ramps both upper level and leading to the new upper levels
2 new elevators
and upper spawn points

This was mostly done again for my jetpack server

give it a try at 69.28.221.213:27015
